    <stitle>AFC G-04902 - Replacement of Pre 2004 Emissions Surge Tanks on 7600, 8600 Models Built Before December 1,
        2003 with Caterpillar C11, C13 Acert Engines; and 9200, 9400, 9900i Models Built Before December 20, 2003 with
