        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>
                    <exhotlnk document="../afcs/AFC04902.pdf" bookname="AFC">Print ready (PDF file) copy of the AFC
                        letter
                    </exhotlnk>
                </para>
                <para>Certain truck models were built with surge tanks that do not meet Caterpillar deareation
                    specifications. To remedy this, a new design surge tank will be installed.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
